<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM4.4.11">
<l>valviṉai tīrkkuṅ kaṇṇaṉai vaṇkuru kūrccaṭa kōpaṉ</l>
<l>colviṉai yālcoṉṉa pāṭa lāyirat tuḷḷivai pattum</l>
<l>nalviṉai yeṉṟukaṟ pārka ṇalaṉiṭai vaikunta naṇṇi</l>
<l>tolviṉai tīravel lārun toḻuteḻa vīṟṟirup pārē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Those who will learn, as good deeds, these ten among the thousand</l>
<l>to be sung, composed through work with words, by Caṭakōpaṉ from</l>
<l>liberal Kurukūr, on Kaṇṇaṉ who ends [the effects of] harsh deeds,</l>
<l>close to Vaikuntam in the middle of goodness they will sit in distinction,</l>
<l>for all to worship [and] rise to, in order to end [the effects of] old deeds.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
